Pretty obvious what it does.
Single target, a few status effects.
The crossbow can only shoot a couple of times before it needs to be reloaded

Reload
Reloads the crossbow with ammo

Basic shot
Uses 1 ammo

Leg shot
Damages and Cripples.  Takes two ammo

Arm shot
Damages and disarms.  Takes two ammo

Flurry
Deals damage to enemies in a 3x1 area. Takes three ammo

Rapid shots
Hits two different targets

Reload Fire Ammo
The next clip deals extra fire damage

Reload and Shoot
Exactly what it says